Class InMemoryTaskDao

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.taskie.db.InMemoryTaskDao
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TaskService

    public class InMemoryTaskDao
extends Object
implements TaskService
    Data access object for Task storing data in memory.

    Use create(FlatService) to create a new DAO.
